== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

==== Global ====

VAAPI support can be enabled system-wide by adding the <code>vaapi</code> value to the <var>USE</var> variable:

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|lang=bash|1=
USE="vaapi"
}}

Enabling VAAPI support will pull in the {{Package|x11-libs/libva}} package, which has the following USE flags:

{{USEflag|package=x11-libs/libva}}

These flags can be adjusted in {{path|[[:/etc/portage/package.use]]}}.

The system needs to be updated if the <var>USE</var> variable has been set to <code>vaapi</code>:

{{Emerge|params+=--changed-use --deep|@world}}

