== Software support ==

=== VLC ===

VLC supports VAAPI natively. Activate the appropriate setting through the preferences menu ({{Path|Tools → Preferences → Input/Codecs → Hardware accelerated decoding}}).

=== mpv ===
mpv also supports the VAAPI acceleration through the command-line option <code>--hwdec=vaapi</code>.

